## Initial Setup

```bash
# 1. Generate config files
kamal init

# 2. Set registry password
export KAMAL_REGISTRY_PASSWORD=your_docker_password

# 3. Set Rails master key
export RAILS_MASTER_KEY=your_rails_master_key

# 4. Setup servers (first time only)
kamal setup

# This will:
# - Install Docker on servers
# - Setup Traefik
# - Setup application
# - Run migrations
# - Start services
```

